    @Mojo(name="webapp-minifier-report",
      threadSafe=true,
      defaultPhase=SITE)
public class WebappMinifierReportMojo
extends org.apache.maven.reporting.AbstractMavenReport
    Generates a report summarizing the minification performed on the web application.
    NOTE: Requires Maven 3.
    Author:
    Lonny
